Introduction:  This git is a storage for debugging python codes,
               not for the entire system!
Date:          20180326
Requirement:   Python3
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Please operate as follows:

1. pip3 install selenium

2. We use Headless Chrome here:
    Chrome-driver链接: https://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html?path=2.37/
        or : 链接:https://pan.baidu.com/s/1-nGRVlpoquCXcixsrfmj-g  密码:23pn
    tar jxvf chromedriver_mac64.zip
    mv chromedriver /usr/local/bin/

3. pip3 install PILLOW

4. AppleScript called by Python:
    1. pip3 install -U pyobjc
    2. Download py-applescript from: [https://pypi.python.org/pypi/py-applescript];
    3. tar jxvf py-applescript-1.0.1.tar.gz
    4. python3 setup.py install

    *.请打开'系统偏好设置'-'安全与隐私'，允许脚本对mac的控制！
    *. Enable Accessibility Inspector (Just for developer):

    refer:
    [1].https://stackoverflow.com/questions/16065162/calling-applescript-from-python-without-using-osascript-or-appscript
    [2].https://github.com/WowJesse/AppleScriptAutoLoginAppStore
    [3].https://pythonhosted.org/pyobjc/install.html
    [4].https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40837086/i-want-the-applescript-to-select-text-field-2-of-sheet-1-of-window-app-store-o?utm_medium=organic&utm_source=google_rich_qa&utm_campaign=google_rich_qa
    [5].https://sspai.com/post/43758?from=timeline
    [6].https://developer.apple.com/library/content/documentation/Accessibility/Conceptual/AccessibilityMacOSX/OSXAXTestingApps.html
    [7].http://www.macosxautomation.com/applescript/uiscripting/

